Package: sibApp
Title: Nonprofit Sector In Brief Dashboard
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Thiyaghessan", "Poongundranar", email = "thiyaghessan@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Urban Institute", role = c("cph", "fnd")))
Description: Shiny dashboard for the Urban Institute's National Center for
    Charitable Statistics (NCCS) presenting headline metrics on the U.S.
    nonprofit sector -- number of organizations, finances, private-foundation
    grantmaking, and donor-advised funds -- with geographic and subsector
    filtering. Deployed via shinyapps.io at
    https://nccs-urban.shinyapps.io/sector-in-brief/.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://nccs-urban.shinyapps.io/sector-in-brief/
Encoding: UTF-8
